data.description: Come take a look at this inviting brick ranch home in Evans which has two bedrooms, one bathroom and a one car attached garage that sits in a cul-de-sac. Let's not forget the charm of the turf backyard for easy maintenance while you enjoy a nice outdoor space. There is NO HOA. Close to shopping & restaurants. You don't want to miss this one!
